Battle of Seven Pines 

May 31, 1862

The Federal offensive over the Virginia Peninsula reachs it's highest peak with the attack onwards to Richmond. Save the Confederacy by defeating the US' attack. The confederate high command at Virginia consideres that you must hold 5 victory locations until the end to get a Brilliant Victory, 4 victory locations to get a single Victory, and 3 to get a Tactical Victory.

25 Turns

